data.description: This is the perfect opportunity to build your dream home on a magnificent Lake Hamilton Lake lot! Or you could complete the remodel on the house that is already there! Beautiful sunsets and sunrises! It's a four (possible five) bedroom and three bath lake home! It has a wood burning fireplace with three bedrooms, one bathroom, kitchen and laundry room downstairs that is a walkout. The upstairs is wired for a kitchen, with a pantry, two bedrooms and two bathrooms, new windows and 9-foot ceilings. The property also has a tool room/shop, a metal carport and wood carport with three parking pads. The water features are so immense! It has two separate floating covered boat slips, a boat launch, two sea-doo ramps, a boat house and two swim docks as well as a large deck to sit and view the lake! Year-round water approximately 40 feet deep by docks. This property has city sewer, city water, lake pump for sprinkler system and propane tank. Arkridge Lake Estates subdivision has a boat ramp and boat dock for use for owners. 100 feet of lake frontage on Lake Hamilton ! Call me today for your private showing!
